1. If the user does not have the ability to haver such as when using a tablet or phone, we must inlcude a media query to detect this so
that our code responds appropriatley.

    @media (max-width: 56.25em), (hover: none) {
    height: auto;
    border-radius: 3px;
    background-color:  $color-white;
    box-shadow: 0 1.5rem 4rem rgba($color-black, .15);
    }
